{"tid":575492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺香港做唔到億萬富豪，就一定要低貧窮線以下嘅人，否則慘過食屎","createTime":"2018-02-28T08:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T09:43:38.000Z","uid":55851,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9be3a5c34ad5240537127eeef1c1e8f73da27c60","tid":575492,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"有錢佬每年剩係退稅已經攞返過億，業界年年都有政府撥錢，官商勾結幾十年冇人阻止到。<br />\n窮撚、蝗、蝻、蛯年年都有錢派，綜援出三糧，再加埋公屋同其他一大堆咩高齡津貼、長生津、傷殘津貼，爽到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係月入10K-30K就等乞米都得，樓你唔會買到，錢你唔會儲到，業你唔會創到，民你又移唔到，但係又做到狗咁，年年交稅補貼鳩鐵，一世為奴，完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cae6359e8f6e6b5fd454e1e331ae95d0e21184","tid":575492,"uid":60668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"講到咁撚慘，做咩唔去搞革命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5e8664b941a044914546c4d929bf50a2dc774d","tid":575492,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38cae6359e8f6e6b5fd454e1e331ae95d0e21184","tid":575492,"uid":60668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"講到咁撚慘，做咩唔去搞革命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n我已經召集左十萬精兵"},{"pid":"b55b4415d52a46f054ba8f205f4015d053774e40","tid":575492,"uid":60615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:23:21.000Z","msg":"正解<br />\n<br />\n但香港地貧窮線三萬太低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fbbc014da920ab60a551b00d5569f1d008b713","tid":575492,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38cae6359e8f6e6b5fd454e1e331ae95d0e21184","tid":575492,"uid":60668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"講到咁撚慘，做咩唔去搞革命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:43:38.000Z","msg":"